# @prisma-admin/core

Core functionality for Prisma Admin - framework-agnostic admin panel generator.

## Installation

```bash
npm install @prisma-admin/core
```

## Usage

The core package provides abstract classes and interfaces that can be implemented by specific framework integrations.

### AdminModelInterface

Main interface for defining admin models:

```typescript
import { AdminModelInterface } from '@prisma-admin/core';

export class MyModelAdmin implements AdminModelInterface {
  modelName = 'MyModel';
  
  getFieldDefinitions() {
    return {
      id: { data_type: 'uuid', label: 'ID' },
      name: { data_type: 'string', label: 'Name' },
      email: { data_type: 'string', label: 'Email' },
    };
  }

  getInlineDefinitions() {
    return {
      relatedItems: {
        model: 'RelatedModel',
        fk_name: 'parentId',
        mode: 'table'
      }
    };
  }
}
```

### BaseAdmin

Abstract base class with common functionality:

```typescript
import { BaseAdmin } from '@prisma-admin/core';

export class MyAdmin extends BaseAdmin {
  // Implementation specific to your framework
}
```

### Utilities

The package also exports utility functions for common operations:

```typescript
import { AdminUtils } from '@prisma-admin/core';

// Validate field definitions
AdminUtils.validateFieldDefinition(field);

// Format values for display
AdminUtils.formatValue(value, fieldType);
```

